<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="es"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>Lista de Jugadores del Betis</title><style>body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;background-color:#c4e699ff;margin:0;padding:20px}h1{text-align:center;color:#006400}.contenedor{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;gap:20px;align-items:stretch}article{background-color:#fff;border:1px solid #ddd;border-radius:10px;width:240px;padding:15px;box-shadow:0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,.1);text-align:center;transition:transform .2s;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:space-between;height:400px}article:hover{transform:scale(1.03)}h3{margin:10px 0 5px;color:#2e8b57;flex-shrink:0}p{margin:5px 0;font-size:14px;flex-grow:1;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;display:-webkit-box;-webkit-line-clamp:6;-webkit-box-orient:vertical}button{margin-top:10px;background-color:#559396ff;color:#fff;border:none;padding:8px 12px;border-radius:5px;cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0}button:hover{background-color:#006400}</style></head><body><img src="img/banner.webp" width="100%" height="500px" loading="lazy" alt="Jugadores del Real Betis"><h1>Jugadores del Real Betis (2025/26)</h1><div class="contenedor"></div></body></html>